snippet.title: Paca Paca Passion 2 Arcade - Full game Playthrough
snippet.description:
Game Setting : Rank - Easy (Default : Normal)
This video has been recorded from My Arcade PCB.(Not MAME)
Music Sequence : Quender Oui - Mask of Guilty - Cool Dancing 2(Perfect : Above 80% on second stage)

[Recording Environment]
For Recording : Arcade PCB(RGB output) → RGB Signal split → XPC-4 (RGB(DVI) Input, DVI Output with DVI-HDMI Cable) →  C875 Live Gamer Portable(HDMI Input+Audio Input, HDMI Output) → LCD Monitor

For Playing : Arcade PCB(RGB output) → RGB Signal split → Nanao 18 inch monitor
